{"tid":1860380,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"深圳市最多確診病例的是鄰近深圳灣口岸的南山區　","createTime":"2020-02-03T15:25:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T09:38:51.000Z","uid":39464,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3283eda2d8c84388e1525b8d75d9b13ed8969926","tid":1860380,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T15:25:03.000Z","msg":"深圳市今日新增19宗新型冠狀病毒感染肺炎病例，累計確診245宗。全市最多病例是鄰近深圳灣口岸的南山區，有50宗。<br />\n<br />\n其次是福田區，有45宗；龍崗區有38宗；羅湖區有17宗。<br />\n<br />\n深圳市衞健委公布，245宗確診病例中，危重病例有5宗，重症病例有24宗。<br />\n<br />\n香港特區政府宣布午夜起關閉4個口岸，包括羅湖、落馬洲支線、皇崗及港澳碼頭，並不包括深圳灣口岸。根據入境處數據，深圳灣是昨日最多內地旅客入境的陸路口岸，有2253人次。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506442-20200203.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506442-20200203.htm&d=oexceJgjEuhZ1NUs%2FbcNdITtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=2075f589\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1506442-20200203.htm&h=2468a699\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1506442-20200203.htm</a>"},{"pid":"fdf494136a76169847c03de10a5bc42b2975801e","tid":1860380,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T15:26:34.000Z","msg":"支那冇樣好嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9452f9ee9d8ad29700834793a0baee91dae89fd7","tid":1860380,"uid":49643,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-03T15:28:17.000Z","msg":"就燒到黎"},{"pid":"f0a2522e182080522c56b5d01a9a686ce0fe6174","tid":1860380,"uid":304769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T09:38:51.000Z","msg":"聽講中旅d車泊嚮紅勘<br />\n私了跨境巴士有無得捻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n見一架拆一架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n另外私了d跨境巴士站有無得捻<br />\n之前中旅比人裝修好似停左一個星期"}]}